data.description: Peace is her name! This beautiful 5bedroom 4bath home sits on 1acre of land in the quite neighborhood of Ginger Lakes. Located close to parks, shopping and the interstate, you have all you need to call this place home. This open floor plan has both formal living and dining, with a two story family room and a kitchen fit for a chef that opens to a keeping room. One bedroom with full bathroom on the main and four bedrooms with a jack and jill bath and two other bathrooms. The master bedroom is a true oasis with views that overlook your backyard, with covered and extended back patio. Make this home your home today.
